svn path=/trunk/koffice/; revision=16515

Torben: Macro Recorder can now record makros on embedded components, too.
That means, start the recorder in KSpread, insert some diagramm, modify
the diagram ( perhaps changing from bars to areas ) und the makro
recorder will even record the change in KDiagramm. NO other office
suite can do that in such a sophisticated manner. At least I dont know one :-)

The Calculator is an addition to KSpread and other components.
Start the calculator from the kspread toolbar and select some cells or ranges of cells and you will see that their value is passed over to the calculator.
